</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph blockId="129.[772,816,2074,2100]" box="[772,816,2074,2100]" pageId="129" pageNumber="130">
<pageNumber ambiguity="1" box="[772,816,2074,2100]" fuzzyness="0" pageId="129" pageNumber="130" score="8913.0" value="130">
<pageTitle box="[772,816,2074,2100]" pageId="129" pageNumber="130">130</pageTitle>
</pageNumber>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="130.[189,1398,267,364]" pageId="130" pageNumber="131">
than distance between apices of R 
<subScript attach="left" box="[589,598,285,299]" fontSize="6" pageId="130" pageNumber="131">1</subScript>
and R 
<subScript attach="left" box="[676,702,285,299]" fontSize="6" pageId="130" pageNumber="131">2+3</subScript>
. R 
<subScript attach="left" box="[737,764,285,299]" fontSize="6" pageId="130" pageNumber="131">4+5</subScript>
and M slightly divergent and evenly arcuate in apical part. Halter with black, elongate knob, contrasting with pale yellow stem. Abdomen lacking gland-like structures. Male terminalia lacking spines; left surstylus without surstylar comb.
</paragraph>
