<subSubSection pageId="130" pageNumber="131" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="130.[189,597,803,829]" box="[189,597,803,829]" pageId="130" pageNumber="131">
<heading bold="true" box="[189,597,803,829]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="130" pageNumber="131" reason="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,597,803,829]" pageId="130" pageNumber="131">Habitat and seasonal occurrence</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="130.[189,1399,850,982]" pageId="130" pageNumber="131">
In 
<collectingCountry box="[220,324,850,876]" name="Thailand" pageId="130" pageNumber="131">Thailand</collectingCountry>
this species is known from two localities, respectively in central and northeastern 
<collectingCountry box="[1287,1394,850,876]" name="Thailand" pageId="130" pageNumber="131">Thailand</collectingCountry>
, with records from the beginning of September to the beginning of October. In 
<collectingCountry box="[1089,1208,885,911]" name="Singapore" pageId="130" pageNumber="131">Singapore</collectingCountry>
this species was taken from secondary forests and mangroves, with all records from only December, whereas in 
<collectingCountry box="[1291,1399,920,946]" name="Malaysia" pageId="130" pageNumber="131">Malaysia</collectingCountry>
this species was taken in July.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
